<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>게시글 작성 - SchoolHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/post-new.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header", { school: typeof school !== "undefined" ? school : null }) %>
  <main class="container">
    <a href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts" class="back-link">
      ← 게시판으로 돌아가기
    </a>

    <h1>게시글 작성</h1>
    <p>작성한 게시글은 관리자 승인 후 공개됩니다.</p>

    <form class="post-form" action="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts" method="POST" autocomplete="off">
      <label>
        카테고리
        <select name="category" required>
          <option value="">카테고리 선택</option>
          <option value="자유">자유</option>
          <option value="질문">질문</option>
          <option value="건의">건의</option>
        </select>
      </label>

      <label>
        제목
        <input
          type="text"
          name="title"
          placeholder="제목을 입력하세요"
          autocomplete="off"
          autocorrect="off"
          spellcheck="false"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <label>
        내용
        <textarea name="content" rows="10" required></textarea>
      </label>

      <label>
        닉네임
        <% if (currentUser) { %>
          <div class="notice-box">
            <strong><%= currentUser.nickname %></strong> 님의 이름으로 작성됩니다.
            로그인 상태에서는 익명 작성이 불가능합니다.
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <label>
            닉네임
            <input
              type="text"
              name="nickname"
              placeholder="비워두면 익명으로 작성됩니다."
              autocomplete="off"
              autocorrect="off"
              spellcheck="false"
            />
          </label>
        <% } %>
      </label>

      <label>
        글 비밀번호
        <input
          type="password"
          name="password"
          placeholder="수정/삭제용 비밀번호"
          autocomplete="new-password"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <button type="submit">제출하기</button>
    </form>
  </main>
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>